"\\subsection*{Combat with Neutral Units}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols
#: sections/recommendations.tex:44
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"During combat with Neutral Units in clash sccenarios, if a player decides to deploy their Units only on one half (left or right one) of the battle board, the player positioning the Neutral Units must follow suit.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: multicols
#: sections/recommendations.tex:48
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Placing Neutral Units far apart only makes the other player waste MPs, and that slows the game down.\n"
"The exception to this rule is when there are three Neutral \\svg{unit_ground} Units to position, as all of them must go the front line.\n"
"See examples that follow.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

